Interface Summary
NodeRenderer<OUTPUT> Interface for classes that render Nodes.
 

Class Summary
AggregateNodeMerger Abstract parent for merging nodes together by aggregating node weights.
CountNodeMerger Merge node weights using count.
EdgeBuilder Configures and builds an Edge.
EdgeWeightEdgeComparator Compares Edge messages by only looking at their weight, and sorts them in decreasing order.
MaxNodeMerger Merge node weights using maximum weight.
MeanNodeMerger Merge nodes using mean.
MinNodeMerger Merge node weights using minimum weight.
NodeAvroFile For reading an avro container file that contains nodes.
NodeBuilder Configures and builds a Node.
NodeCopier Efficiently perform multiple deep-copies of Nodes.
NodeMerger Abstract parent for merging nodes together.
NodeUtils Utility class for avro Node messages.
SumNodeMerger Merge node weights using sum.
TargetLabelEdgeComparator Sorts edges by target label lexicographically.
TargetLabelNumericEdgeComparator Sorts edges by target label numerically.
 

Enum Summary
AggregateNodeMerger.MergeNodeAggregateType Supported aggregate types.
